Description: JACK/PulseAudio volume control via OSC for CUEMS
 jack-volume is a JACK and PulseAudio client for controlling audio volume
 of multiple channels via OSC (Open Sound Control).
 .
 This package provides:
  - jack-volume: JACK audio volume control daemon
  - pa-volume: PulseAudio volume control daemon
  - jvctl: GTK3 GUI for manual volume control
  - udp_dispatcher: UDP packet dispatcher for OSC
  - generic_connector: OSC protocol bridge
 .
 Part of the CUEMS (Cue Management System) audio infrastructure.
